{"tid":2154033,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【OFFER 報分區】ATU HK","createTime":"2020-08-13T01:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T16:09:24.000Z","uid":77916,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bc05116f7c0892d9e12355fa1dd89d83756c622d","tid":2154033,"uid":77916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:48:10.000Z","msg":"恭喜所有收倒JUPAS offer既同學。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩你地幫忙做一樣野，就係去ATU HK 報你既offer，不論你接受與否。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.atu.hk/results/2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atu.hk%2Fresults%2F2020&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzqGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=271338d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.atu.hk/results/2020</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個動作可以幫倒兩批人：<br />\n1. Appeal之後成功升grade既人。佢地可以睇住今年既真實收生分數去決定報乜野。<br />\n2. 之後年份想入同一個program既中學生。佢地可以喺 upper quartile / median 等數據以外，睇埋收offer既人既實際分數，有加乘科目囉咩grade，有無interview 等等。<br />\n<br />\n報Grade用你少少時間，造福多人，懇請收offer既考生幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n最後，記得繼續撐《蘋果》。"},{"pid":"96918018d6f4001fa16611aadc60e601ca83dd6e","tid":2154033,"uid":190639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:25:13.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n依幾年好似少咗好多人report咁"},{"pid":"a53bc4d23ccd128d6a6e652f5c3f30abd2edfc43","tid":2154033,"uid":29859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d3b3ae7fb424d3386b6b3311e9ec9ec3e74ae8cd","tid":2154033,"uid":302897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f17395b8b005969f9f72411daf8d5a40455d390","tid":2154033,"uid":305544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"造福後人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99bc9aada0d22ac5edabd788664e9984d6fe4e3","tid":2154033,"uid":46823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T02:52:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾未來嘅同學做參考"},{"pid":"4e237c912